p;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+the+Folklore+Institute&amp;rft.atitle=American+Anthropology+and+the+Development+of+Folklore+Scholarship%3A+1890-1920&amp;rft.volume=10&amp;rft.issue=1-2&amp;rft.pages=23-39&amp;rft.date=1973&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F3813878&amp;rft.aulast=Darnell&amp;rft.aufirst=Regna&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABoasian+anthropology\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Epps, Patience L.; Webster, Anthony K.; Woodbury, Anthony C. (2017). \"A Holistic Humanities of Speaking: Franz Boas and the Continuing Centrality of Texts\". <i>International Journal of American Linguistics</i>. <b>83</b> (1): 41\u201378. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1086/689547\">10.1086/689547</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=International+Journal+of+American+Linguistics&amp;rft.atitle=A+Holistic+Humanities+of+Speaking%3A+Franz+Boas+and+the+Continuing+Centrality+of+Texts&amp;rft.volume=83&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=41-78&amp;rft.date=2017&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1086%2F689547&amp;rft.aulast=Epps&amp;rft.aufirst=Patience+L.&amp;rft.au=Webster%2C+Anthony+K.&amp;rft.au=Woodbury%2C+Anthony+C.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABoasian+anthropology\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Andersen, Chris; O'Brien, Jean M., eds. (2016). <i>Sources and Methods in Indigenous Studies</i>. New York: Routledge.</cite><span title=\"